{
  "stem": "428.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this is that Polish--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I left, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to-- I came to Krakau-- to Krakau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know that in Prokocim, in that camp in Prokocim, I have my-- oh, I see, I forgot to tell.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had my sister's husband was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I walk in by myself into that camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, when I came back to Poland, when I came back to Poland, they know that they-- he was in the same town from where I come.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They know that-- what was his name?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot his name already-- is in Prokocim in a camp, that Polack know about him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Polack know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When-- that Polack, one more thing, that Polack, when I was walking in that town, Prokocim, going to work in the morning, so that Polack, came with that little girl.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't come in close when they took us to work, but that little girl came with a little second bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She gave me that, little Polack, Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She's alive now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She's in Canada.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Her father wasn't-- because grown people, they didn't let stay close to the Jews when they took them to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that little girl, she was smart enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was playing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when I was walking, she handed me bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's a lot of things what to tell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And some of the Polish people was-- was good too, because in the places where we was working, when we came in the morning to work, it was laying bread on the ground.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They used to go at night and throw away bread, that when we come to work-- yes, some of them, they was nice, Polish people, yeah.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
